 The "muxr" block selects which of the 4 inputs ( D, R, uPC, TOS) are to
 be fed to the tri-state driver and also includes the tri-state-driver.

 In testing this block, we select all 1's and all 0's for each of the 
 following inputs :

 (a)	D

 (b)	R

 (c)	uPC

 (d)	top of stack

 We also test the condition when no input is selected and the output is zero.